{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f24f5301a7","title":"对学术问题的不同意见不应禁止谈论","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0576674460","index":0,"year":1956,"month":2,"day":19,"articleId":"f24f5301a7"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji36","name":"毛泽东全集第36卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/36-OCR.pdf"},{"id":"wenji7","name":"毛泽东文集第七卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/wenji7.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji36":{"comments":[{"id":"ef2fd37201","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"f24f5301a7","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东在中共中央宣传部1956年2月1日关于是否要向苏联共产党有关方面反映苏联学者在中国参观时讲的一些话给中央的报告上写的批语。"},{"id":"c3a63ecd52","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"f24f5301a7","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指当时在中国讲学的一位苏联学者，在去访问广东省中山县孙中山故居途中，向中国陪同人员谈到他对毛泽东《新民主主义论》中关于孙中山先生的世界观的论点的不同着法。"},{"id":"8095fcb0ac","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"f24f5301a7","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"无金（1899—1968），苏联哲学家、科学院院士。当时任苏联驻中国大使。"}],"contents":[{"id":"ad359487d2","type":"title","text":"对学术问题的不同意见不应禁止谈论！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"f24f5301a7"},{"id":"ef2fd37201","type":"paragraph","text":"刘、周、陈、彭真、小平、陈伯达阅，退定一办。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"f24f5301a7"},{"id":"c3a63ecd52","type":"paragraph","text":"我认为这种自由谈论，不应当去禁止。这是对学术思想的不同意见，什么人都可以谈论，无所谓损害威信。因此，不要向无金谈此事。如果国内对此类学术问题和任何领导人有不同意见，也不应加以禁止。如果企图禁止，那是完全错误的。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"f24f5301a7"},{"id":"8095fcb0ac","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"f24f5301a7"},{"id":"8147761be3","type":"paragraph","text":"二月十九日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"f24f5301a7"}],"page":{"id":"a020f479b3","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"f24f5301a7","start":221,"end":221}},"wenji7":{"comments":[{"id":"0c591544b4","publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"f24f5301a7","index":2,"part_index":1,"offset":9,"text":"指当时在中国讲学的一位苏联学者，在去访问广东中山县孙中山故居途中，向中国陪同人员谈到他对毛泽东《新民主主义论》中关于孙中山的世界观的论点的不同看法。"},{"id":"ac0dcb08d1","publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"f24f5301a7","index":1,"part_index":0,"offset":16,"text":"这是毛泽东在中共中央宣传部一九五六年二月一日关于是否要向苏联共产党有关方面反映苏联学者在中国参观时讲的一些话给中央的报告上写的批语。"},{"id":"bfeeb1a2fe","publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"f24f5301a7","index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"根据手稿刊印。"},{"id":"f2cde13a5e","publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"f24f5301a7","index":3,"part_index":1,"offset":55,"text":"尤金（一八九九——一九六八），苏联哲学家、科学院院士。当时任苏联驻中国大使。"}],"contents":[{"id":"0c591544b4","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"f24f5301a7"},{"id":"6c16336d67","type":"title","text":"对学术问题的不同意见不应禁止谈论","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"f24f5301a7"},{"id":"ac0dcb08d1","type":"paragraph","text":"我认为这种自由谈论，不应当去禁止。这是对学术思想的不同意见，什么人都可以谈论，无所谓损害威信。因此，不要向尤金谈此事。如果国内对此类学术问题和任何领导人有不同意见，也不应加以禁止。如果企图禁止，那是完全错误的。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"f24f5301a7"},{"id":"f2cde13a5e","type":"paragraph","text":"二月十九日","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"f24f5301a7"}],"page":{"id":"8d013b01e1","publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"f24f5301a7","start":18,"end":18}}}},"__N_SSG":true}